com.cyberfront.crdt.operation

  • Packages that use com.cyberfront.crdt.operation 
    Package Description
    com.cyberfront.crdt
    The com.cyberfront.crdt package includes the core classes to build and manage a commutative CRDT for managing JSON document updates using the JSON Patch standard.
    com.cyberfront.crdt.operation  
    com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.simulation
    The com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.simulation contains a collection of classes which are intended to perform stress testing on the functionality of the commutative CRDT implementation specified elsewhere in the class library.
    com.cyberfront.crdt.unittest  
  • Classes in com.cyberfront.crdt.operation used by com.cyberfront.crdt 
    Class Description
    Operation
    The Operation class is intended to be a base / abstract class for the set of operations which would normally be expected to be performed on a persistence store.
    Operation.OperationType
    The Enum OperationType lists the types of operations which comprise the types of operations which can be performed on JSON objects
    OperationManager
    This is the base class for wrapping AbstractOperations.
